title: Current 93 Live at Union Chapel Feb08 2014 bootleg FLAC
description:
Current 93 Live at Union Chapel, London
February 8 2014

Bootleg recording
Sorry for lower quality, but for those who missed this, I had to upload...

First performance was MacGillvray, then Shirley Collins' first performance in 35 years.

Then Current 93 played their new album (part 1), after credits intermezzo (part 2), there was few oldies like Black Ships Ate The Sky, Lucifer over London and Sad Go Round.
